sending him flying. He aimed his cannon and fired it at Arrow 4 times,
hitting each time. He kept heading towards Termitron. Airbomber pulled a
grenade and threw it at Arrow. Arrow transformed and started to stand up
wearily.

Grenade Timer: 3, 2, 1,

